2. âœ… All stats cards MUST use: p-8 rounded-2xl (NOT p-6)
3. âœ… Section headings MUST use font-display class
4. âœ… Data tables MUST have hover:shadow-hover on rows
5. âœ… Charts MUST use primary gradient colors
6. âœ… Loading states: Skeleton loaders with proper spacing
7. âœ… All metric numbers MUST use font-display for emphasis

